cb0d601dd32e7555ceea7da7b75bed4cf9b7","tid":2014992,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b0741f199e183623252e7397a39e1273484d1701","tid":2014992,"uid":2819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"😖我起荃灣做野嫁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，唔好害人呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:48:50.000Z","msg":"咁都抵死"},{"pid":"3b4ece4e3de2be7f28f0d9d34ba36d201b5e1163","tid":2014992,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"樓主去完卓明樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29ad02df7db5217911f09451a70609da719ad74","tid":2014992,"uid":169400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf1adb45508b0361aa6de0dccef2a8105b1de30","tid":2014992,"uid":150363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:23:19.000Z","msg":"提一下，大家唔好透露自己住邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"我呢就住係香港既"},{"pid":"62de1d2c0f2e90ee35c591ab77e1f4169c0bb25f","tid":2014992,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】十四歲少年於「沙士」肆虐期間，在愚人節當天盜用《明報新聞網》的格式，在互聯網上散播「香港成為疫埠」的假消息，被警方以《檢疫及防疫條例》票控，早前承認控罪。 <br />\n總裁判官李瀚良鑑於被告沒有嚴重刑事動機，昨日輕判他接受十二個月社署監管令，不留案底，又勸勉他應將電腦知識用於有建設性的地方。<br />\n<br />\n充公硬碟免留案底 <br />\n暑假後將升讀中四的被告，由父親及班主任陪同到九龍城法院，其父聞判後表示日後會加緊看管兒子。 <br />\n裁判官表示，本案是一場惡作劇，但少年沒有嚴重刑事動機，故輕判他接受社署監管，學習使用電腦的正確態度，為期十二個月。裁判官並引用《少年犯條例》撤銷其控罪，免留案底，但下令充公其電腦硬碟。 <br />\n控罪指被告於今年四月一日，明知而提供有關傳染病的虛假資料，即訛稱行政長官公布因「沙士」未能受控，宣布香港成為疫埠。事發於愚人節，被告從互聯網下載《明報新聞網》的格式，將內容改頭換面，訛稱特首將香港列為疫埠，市民不能外出，再將假消息上載到自己的網頁。 <br />\n結果，假消息在數小時內被廣泛流傳，引起風波，不少超級市場出現搶購潮，衞生署更急忙開記者會澄清。警方追查下，拘捕涉案被告。 <br />\n案件編號：FLS700017/2003<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20030805/3453559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030805%2F3453559&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9Nacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=6838b9a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030805%2F3453559&h=7d87360f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20030805/3453559</a>"},{"pid":"5517020f8dc73b7f8f6d5b16d1f89fa68e3c14fd","tid":2014992,"uid":947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"人在荃灣now<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64b29fdb7ee33680f8255de03f99187909f906c","tid":2014992,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:53:24.000Z","msg":"快d叫連仔del po"},{"pid":"e71f296646947dba890ed3231377c8b15aadd3fc","tid":2014992,"uid":300625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1dbf30afa44abb00080c1b9b21e5d11444c7fdc5","tid":2014992,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}